_sText:
DE_Cemetery by Kev_Boy
kevindesmet@yahoo.com

Background: A month after 6-6-06, the 19th angel guarding hell fell, and the dead walked the earth... on zombie servers.

Terrorists: We must bomb the holiest places on this British country-side cemetery. For here lurks great evil and if we do not destroy it, its overwhelming aura will soon cause the dead to walk the earth, for hell is full!

Counter-Terrorists: When killing a dozen hostages in another screw-up... we decided to stop by for a quick prayer, while we got reports of superstitious terrorists wanting to bomb this place!

In the laughable event the dead would walk the earth like they proclaim, longing to 'swallow our souls'... Come Get Some!
